OL,3,CNumber of school suspensions for
OL,4,Cchildren being racist doubles
OL,6,FThe number of exclusions for children
OL,7,Fbeing racist in Government of Jersey
OL,8,Fschools has more than doubled in two
OL,9,Facademic years.
OL,11,FA total of 27 instances of racist
OL,12,Fabuse led to student suspensions
OL,13,Facross 2024-25 - compared to 12 in
OL,14,F2022-23, according to a Freedom of
OL,15,FInformation request.
OL,17,FEducation Minister, Deputy Rob Ward,
OL,18,Fsays the marked rise is troubling but
OL,19,Falso demonstrates how teachers are
OL,20,Fcommitted to stamping it out.
