OL,6,FHe explains: "We take this very
OL,7,Fseriously. While the rise in
OL,8,Fsuspensions is concerning, it shows
OL,9,Fschools are taking decisive action and
OL,10,Fit is also due to a more accurate
OL,11,Fsystem of reporting suspensions.
OL,13,F"Racism in any form is unacceptable,
OL,14,Fand every child and young person has
OL,15,Fthe right to feel safe and respected
OL,16,Fin their learning environment."
