OL,6,FDeputy Ward adds: "Any incident is one
OL,7,Ftoo many and we are committed to
OL,8,Ftackling racial abuse with mandatory
OL,9,Fpolicies, staff training and
OL,10,Feducation, to ensure every child can
OL,11,Flearn and thrive in an inclusive and
OL,12,Frespectful environment.
OL,14,F"Racism has no place in our schools or
OL,15,Fin society and it is a learned
OL,16,Fbehaviour. We all have a part to play
OL,17,Fto ensure children and young people
OL,18,Fdon't learn that behaviour."
